    <h2>Common Commercial Roofing Estimating Mistakes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Underestimating tear-off costs</strong> — Existing roof removal can add $1.50-$3.00 per sq ft</li>
      <li><strong>Missing flashing details</strong> — Complex parapet walls and curbs require significant labor</li>
      <li><strong>Ignoring weather delays</strong> — Budget 10-15% additional days for weather</li>
      <li><strong>Forgetting disposal fees</strong> — Dumpster rental and disposal fees add $500-$2,000 per project</li>
    </ul>

